When it will come to destruction,

01:04.796 --> 01:07.146
it will be used as earthquakes.

01:07.166 --> 01:09.496
They will, it will act as earthquakes.

01:09.505 --> 01:11.808
America is that whole portion,

01:11.825 --> 01:14.325
it is all Andes from top to bottom,

01:14.325 --> 01:17.418
and all that will be shattered by earthquakes.

01:17.418 --> 01:23.120
So, these two forces will act
more at the time of destruction.

01:23.150 --> 01:26.250
So, one has to be careful about it.

01:26.270 --> 01:31.340
Because, you see, Bolivia,
say Peru and all these places,

01:31.362 --> 01:33.862
these people went from here.

01:33.862 --> 01:36.899
They killed so many of these people.

01:36.922 --> 01:40.989
So many of these races were killed completely.

01:41.009 --> 01:43.149
Then dead bodies were there.

01:43.159 --> 01:45.909
Killing is very bad, because when you kill a person,

01:45.929 --> 01:53.029
that person cannot take birth and
hangs in the air and becomes a bhoot.

01:53.054 --> 01:55.029
So, they have overpowered Americans.

01:55.029 --> 01:56.649
That’s why Americans are like that.

01:56.661 --> 02:01.589
You see, they killed all the people
from New York to the whole of America

02:01.585 --> 02:04.289
was all people who were aboriginal.

02:04.289 --> 02:06.469
So, they have possessed them also.

02:06.469 --> 02:08.469
And in the same way in the South it’s happening.

02:08.463 --> 02:10.009
So, it is all, again,

02:10.017 --> 02:12.749
though it is right-sided but it’s supraconscious,

02:12.752 --> 02:15.252
all supraconscious things.

02:15.252 --> 02:17.349
So, they have to be very careful now.

02:17.349 --> 02:19.019
They have to take to Sahaja Yoga

02:19.019 --> 02:21.519
and those who will be taking to
Sahaja Yoga will be only saved.

02:21.519 --> 02:24.019
The rest will be destroyed,

02:24.019 --> 02:28.739
because Andes will act as a
supraconscious thing for destruction.

02:28.739 --> 02:31.239
And Fujiyama and all that, will have,

02:31.239 --> 02:34.623
not, they will have those, what you call them?

02:34.623 --> 02:37.123
Volcanoes.

