03:00.995 --> 03:01.620
Kailash

03:01.620 --> 03:05.475
Yes. Sahasrara.

03:05.496 --> 03:07.665
Yes, fontanelle bone

03:07.665 --> 03:12.625
And this is the plate of the Ekadesha.

03:12.627 --> 03:13.875
All right!

03:13.908 --> 03:22.578
Now all the, even this Zermatt and this alps
and all that is in the same.

03:22.583 --> 03:24.034
In the same line?

03:24.043 --> 03:26.103
On the right and left side, both sides.

03:26.103 --> 03:28.603
(Unclear) Argentina we have all these on that

03:28.603 --> 03:31.103
