03:31.103 --> 03:35.853
But, on both the sides, we have got Andes

03:35.858 --> 03:40.051
and this side, we have got Fujiyama and all this.

03:40.080 --> 03:50.507
Out of these two, the left-sided one is the Andes.

03:50.507 --> 03:54.134
I‘ve treated it as Andes as left-sided actually,

03:54.153 --> 03:58.127
because the sun rises from this side,

03:58.153 --> 04:00.653
and the right-sided one should be

04:00.653 --> 04:03.747
the Japanese according to Sahaja Yoga style.

04:03.747 --> 04:06.247
But in the thing, if you see,

04:06.247 --> 04:09.876
this is right and this is left.

04:09.877 --> 04:13.816
Now, what has happened is that

04:13.827 --> 04:22.008
the right-sided people like Spanish and all that,

04:22.011 --> 04:23.660
went down there

04:23.660 --> 04:26.460
and killed so many of these people,

04:26.475 --> 04:29.926
who were all right-sided too.

04:29.935 --> 04:32.435
So the whole thing we should call it as right-sided

04:32.435 --> 04:34.935
now. The Andes as right-sided.

04:34.935 --> 04:36.506
Because right-sided people

04:36.506 --> 04:39.006
will be punished by the right-sided defects

04:39.006 --> 04:42.016
and left will be punished by the left-sided defects.

04:42.006 --> 04:44.506
So, because the right-sided people have gone there

04:44.506 --> 04:47.486
and have killed the right-sided people,

04:47.486 --> 04:49.076
the right-sided people there

04:49.076 --> 04:50.976
have overpowered these people.

04:50.976 --> 04:52.886
That’s why the speed is there,

04:52.886 --> 04:55.386
and the Americans are, you see, like this

04:55.386 --> 04:59.366
all very violent all these things, because of that.

04:59.357 --> 05:03.146
Now all these things put together forms this,

05:03.125 --> 05:05.236
the Andes, you see, is there, standing,

05:05.215 --> 05:07.715
waiting for its chance.

05:07.715 --> 05:10.955
And when the things will be horrible absolutely,

05:10.987 --> 05:14.127
there won’t be any atomic bomb blast or anything.

05:14.157 --> 05:18.846
These, themselves will have earthquakes.

05:18.846 --> 05:23.717
Now, earthquake is the quality of Mother Earth.

05:23.717 --> 05:26.217
And she will assert through these.

05:26.217 --> 05:30.369
And on the right-hand side…

05:30.387 --> 05:32.887
Actually, it is actually not on the right-hand side,

05:32.887 --> 05:35.387
but now it’s the left-hand side

05:35.387 --> 05:39.818
of these Japanese what will happen…

05:39.819 --> 05:42.788
Because they were made into left-hand sided,

05:42.788 --> 05:45.137
because they were given these drugs,

05:45.138 --> 05:47.097
opium, this thing, that thing.

05:47.107 --> 05:49.017
So they became left-sided.

05:49.017 --> 05:54.317
Now, these left-handed people
will be finished with volcanoes

05:54.356 --> 05:56.687
There will be volcanoes. There will be typhoons,

05:56.696 --> 05:57.923
they’ll be finished.

05:57.926 --> 06:00.426
While on this side, the

06:00.426 --> 06:03.443
people who have been following

06:03.466 --> 06:07.663
these all wrong things will be finished with earthquakes.

06:07.673 --> 06:10.173
And all these places like,

06:10.173 --> 06:13.345
you can say, the west coast...

06:13.373 --> 06:18.805
The west coast of America is very dangerous,

06:18.803 --> 06:24.505
because there were so many
atrocities done by Americans.

06:24.505 --> 06:27.005
They cannot get away with it,

06:27.005 --> 06:30.188
so themselves they’ll be finished
because they’ll become lunatics,

06:30.240 --> 06:36.438
mad and apart from that, the Mother Earth
itself will finish them, partly.

06:38.068 --> 06:41.801
Now on the right-hand side,

06:41.818 --> 06:45.811
I think volcanoes will be finished this way,

06:45.811 --> 06:48.311
at the destruction time they’ll be used….

06:48.311 --> 06:51.471
But just now as far as now is concerned

06:51.503 --> 06:55.491
we have to see how many people we can bring out.

06:55.513 --> 06:59.851
If the number of Sahaja yogis
increases in those areas,

06:59.874 --> 07:03.811
then maybe, that Mother will be pacified.

07:06.599 --> 07:09.099
The same that was written in the Bible,

07:09.646 --> 07:12.146
The same is written in the Bible,

07:12.146 --> 07:19.556
when God wants to come and
kill the Sodom and Gomorrah

07:19.543 --> 07:23.056
and Abraham perhaps asked to God,

07:23.066 --> 07:25.296
“but God if there is ten good people,

07:25.310 --> 07:27.116
what will you do?”

07:27.116 --> 07:29.616
and God said “O.K., I will save them,”

07:29.616 --> 07:33.824
and then Abraham say, “but if there
are nine people, good people?”

07:33.856 --> 07:36.124
and God say, “O.K. I will save them.”

07:36.146 --> 07:39.626
so he asked, "And if there's just one good people?"

07:39.625 --> 07:43.025
Then God said: “O.K., I will save that town.”

07:43.025 --> 07:45.145
And now Mother, are we the same?

07:45.155 --> 07:47.655
Now we are thousands.

07:47.655 --> 07:50.155
But in the Bible, it is written only how many?

07:50.155 --> 07:53.528
Hundred and forty-four thousand.

07:53.535 --> 07:58.608
That's all?

08:01.545 --> 08:04.845
We’re about reaching that number,

08:04.857 --> 08:07.357
one hundred and forty-four thousand.

08:10.467 --> 08:12.967
Only!

08:15.407 --> 08:16.797
It's written.

08:16.807 --> 08:18.547
It is written in the Bible.

08:18.547 --> 08:22.137
Shri Mataji, does it mean that the Last Judgement

08:22.149 --> 08:27.127
at the time of destruction will manifest in these forms,

08:27.155 --> 08:28.884
earthquake and volcanoes?

08:28.908 --> 08:31.024
Of course, that will be there.

08:31.038 --> 08:33.144
So many things will happen

08:33.138 --> 08:35.313
and people will be killed and destroyed.

08:35.320 --> 08:37.820
And then they'll be put to the last thing,

08:37.842 --> 08:39.343
they will go to hell.

08:39.392 --> 08:41.892
People will descend to the hell.

08:41.892 --> 08:44.392
You see, what will happen on this Earth only,

08:44.392 --> 08:46.242
people will become mad,

08:46.261 --> 08:51.342
they’ll start eating faeces, Naraka
they will be creating for themselves.

08:51.342 --> 08:57.042
Now only the way, say, they are following Rajneesh.

08:57.042 --> 08:58.962
What are they doing?

08:58.962 --> 09:01.462
It's Naraka.

09:01.462 --> 09:03.761
That’s how they’ll be punished.

09:03.762 --> 09:06.262
And those who are described now, one thousand...

09:06.262 --> 09:09.551
one hundred and forty-four
thousand is a very small number.

09:12.871 --> 09:17.980
Can I ask a question about those people
who get killed, Mother and become bhoots?

09:18.040 --> 09:21.380
Is there never any chance?

09:21.404 --> 09:23.270
Difficult.

09:23.300 --> 09:24.710
Those who are killed might be,

09:24.731 --> 09:28.320
but those who are possessed...

09:28.361 --> 09:33.410
You see, what has happened that those
who are killed are reborn again.

09:33.430 --> 09:36.410
And some, those who are...

09:36.410 --> 09:39.431
have been killing are also reborn.

09:39.455 --> 09:42.915
So there is a chance for such people.

09:42.945 --> 09:46.475
But those who are killed are possessing people

09:46.473 --> 09:48.973
who killed them.

09:53.953 --> 09:56.003
Why did they kill?

09:56.003 --> 09:57.939
They had no business.

09:57.993 --> 10:01.409
“Thou shalt not kill.”

10:01.423 --> 10:03.923
I mean after all, if you do not

10:03.923 --> 10:09.440
follow one rule and regulation
of your hopeless government,

10:09.426 --> 10:11.926
you are punished. What about God?

10:11.926 --> 10:16.350
He said “thou shalt not kill” and you have killed.

10:16.382 --> 10:18.882
So, you should not be punished?

10:18.882 --> 10:21.382
I was thinking of those that got killed,

10:21.382 --> 10:25.076
those who were killed, the victims.

10:25.087 --> 10:28.076
If they are reborn they will not,

10:28.076 --> 10:33.663
but if they are taking a revenge, then how to save?

10:33.683 --> 10:36.853
And they can choose?

10:36.883 --> 10:39.863
They can choose.

10:39.873 --> 10:43.573
If they want, they should take
their birth, get realisation.

10:43.573 --> 10:48.304
But they are trying to become bhoots.

10:53.944 --> 10:57.267
The idea of revenge should not be there.

10:57.284 --> 11:01.254
Now, you see, Indians have only this sense, actually.

11:01.254 --> 11:04.404
How much Britishers have tortured Indians,

11:04.428 --> 11:07.384
you have no idea.

11:07.418 --> 11:10.078
I mean, I cannot tell you how much they have done.

11:10.108 --> 11:13.188
I can only tell you about my own family,

11:13.198 --> 11:18.238
that my father’s all houses,
everything was taken away.

11:18.238 --> 11:22.548
We were living in palaces, we started living in huts.

11:22.549 --> 11:24.858
Cars, everything, all ornaments,

11:24.855 --> 11:27.865
everything of my mother was taken away.

11:27.895 --> 11:29.525
Only we had one big...

11:29.535 --> 11:34.195
mother had a big family gold thing we called Vaijayanti mala,

11:34.225 --> 11:36.105
that’s the only thing that she had hidden,

11:36.149 --> 11:39.495
which she pawned and on that she educated us.

11:39.462 --> 11:41.305
To me, they have beaten,

11:41.315 --> 11:43.555
they have given me electric shocks.

11:43.565 --> 11:48.915
They put me on the ice slabs.

11:48.938 --> 11:52.465
I was a young girl of 18-19 years, you see.

11:52.474 --> 11:54.734
To so many people they have tortured like this.

11:54.730 --> 12:00.904
Oh, they have tortured and tortured
to such an extent, you have no idea.

12:00.904 --> 12:06.477
But... and raping, prostitution,
everything they did to Indians.

12:06.504 --> 12:08.447
But Indians don’t hate English.

12:08.484 --> 12:10.984
They don’t hate them.

12:10.984 --> 12:14.174
They are very kind. If English go there, you see

12:14.176 --> 12:19.924
some English barristers went in to India and
the holiday was given to the High Court.

12:21.836 --> 12:24.336
They are so respectful, but when English now,

12:24.356 --> 12:26.856
when the Indians, because they misbehaved

12:26.836 --> 12:29.271
and they brought so many Indians with them.

12:29.292 --> 12:31.481
Now they were given British passports

12:31.502 --> 12:35.771
and sent as slaves to East Africa to work there.

12:35.770 --> 12:41.751
But when East Africa became independent they had British passports, so they came as Britishers.

12:41.772 --> 12:44.272
Now they are treated as immigrants in England.

12:44.272 --> 12:46.341
Think of it.

12:46.362 --> 12:50.446
Actually, they have only British
passport, they have no other passport.

12:50.446 --> 12:53.666
And 80% of Indians are like that.

12:53.671 --> 12:58.799
10% are students and 10% may be Pakistanis.

12:58.789 --> 13:00.159
Can you imagine?

13:00.159 --> 13:02.659
And see the condition of Indians in England,

13:02.659 --> 13:05.159
the way these English feel about them.

13:05.159 --> 13:10.969
So, naturally, one would feel very
embittered with them. Isn’t it?

13:10.969 --> 13:14.879
But I have never seen any Indian
criticising English people.

13:14.902 --> 13:18.262
My husband once said it is Indians who are responsible,

13:18.272 --> 13:22.662
they behave in such a manner, they wash
their clothes, they hang them outside.

13:22.670 --> 13:23.652
This, that!

13:23.660 --> 13:26.160
He will always blame the Indians;

13:26.160 --> 13:28.232
they don’t know how to eat on a table,

13:28.232 --> 13:33.498
they use their hands, this that. Indians!

13:33.523 --> 13:35.510
Not embittered at all!

13:35.518 --> 13:37.808
They are the only people who have really forgiven.

13:37.838 --> 13:40.338
There is no embitterment and you know, in India

13:40.338 --> 13:42.838
it’s a law, unwritten law.

13:42.838 --> 13:47.574
I was on the censor board, that no
film can be made against the English.

13:47.591 --> 13:48.684
Nothing!

13:48.701 --> 13:52.224
No film is made about our freedom,
independence or about Gandhi.

13:52.224 --> 13:56.758
This is an Englishman who made it.

13:56.768 --> 13:59.268
We were not allowed to do that.

14:02.234 --> 14:11.533
There was a big series, very popular series showing how awful the British had been to the Indians, which was on in England.

14:11.564 --> 14:15.144
They always tried to debase
Indians, to make fun of them.

14:15.144 --> 14:24.313
Everybody’s horrified, because we
don’t know. We just read in the books

14:24.343 --> 14:26.843
What is the name of the series?

14:26.923 --> 14:31.083
The Jewel in the Crown! It’s called “The Jewel in the Crown”.

14:31.100 --> 14:36.033
It is about the last days of the British
Raj. And it is horrible. You can't watch.

14:36.028 --> 14:37.193
I mean, what do they show there.

14:37.185 --> 14:40.605
They show bestiality, they show absolute cruelty,

14:40.638 --> 14:45.785
beating some boy with sticks, accusing
him of raping a girl that he never did.

14:45.812 --> 14:46.937
Who? English?

14:46.951 --> 14:47.707
English, yes.

14:47.720 --> 14:48.467
They did?

14:48.480 --> 14:52.697
It shows the English in a very bad light. Very bad!

14:57.448 --> 15:01.797
Good, it's being at least exposed.

15:01.817 --> 15:04.317
Somebody must have talked about it.

15:04.317 --> 15:09.717
When we watched the film of Gandhi, in
Delhi, when you took us to see that movie,

15:09.699 --> 15:13.454
at the half time, everybody walked out.

15:13.474 --> 15:18.244
About forty of the British Sahaja yogis
were just absolutely like stunned mullets

15:18.244 --> 15:20.104
they couldn’t move.

15:20.123 --> 15:21.314
That is nothing,

15:21.350 --> 15:24.514
They have shown nothing, compared
to what people have seen.

15:24.514 --> 15:27.214
This series is much more brutal than that.

15:27.244 --> 15:29.744
Watching it was so horrible.

15:29.744 --> 15:30.655
I heard about it.

15:30.655 --> 15:31.835
Horrible.

15:31.835 --> 15:37.385
And you see now, as they were saying
there were no arches or bridges.

15:37.425 --> 15:40.875
Now, the British must have
removed everything that was there.

15:40.875 --> 15:44.705
They never respected anything. Even now
they have no respect for our culture,

15:44.723 --> 15:47.945
for our music, for anything.

15:47.958 --> 15:51.015
They haven’t got brains to understand.

15:53.366 --> 15:56.326
In such ego!

15:56.332 --> 16:00.006
Shri Mataji, you were saying this
afternoon that a lot of the culture, and

16:00.015 --> 16:07.742
history and architecture and so on, of India
predates, so much, a lot of the west.

16:07.776 --> 16:15.395
Most! I mean, I told them that
these people say Greeks brought us all these things,

16:15.416 --> 16:20.775
but, they have not seen that in India we have something called Ajanta Caves.

16:20.775 --> 16:21.895
Made in the caves!

16:21.904 --> 16:30.364
Caves mean like palaces, huge and
one stone, huge, for miles like that.

16:30.376 --> 16:33.534
I said, if we have learned from the Greeks,

16:33.534 --> 16:37.556
why don’t the Greeks have something like that.

16:37.564 --> 16:39.536
They don’t have anything.

16:39.536 --> 16:45.316
The kind of art we have in our country, you don’t
find it anywhere in the whole world, I think.

16:45.330 --> 16:53.058
I mean this now... I've said it of
course, (unclear) but it is built from down upwards.

16:57.818 --> 17:02.808
It is a cave, you see, from top downwards, in ten centuries.

