Excuse me, Mother, do you want me to translate
for the people that doesn’t understand?

17:09.030 --> 17:11.530
Please, I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

18:06.718 --> 18:09.218
All the engineering, everything
had to be calculated from...

18:14.239 --> 18:23.419
She’s explained that, what you explained today
that we started from the roof and then we go down...

18:23.433 --> 18:26.436
Like you were explaining today to this fellow.

18:26.456 --> 18:28.956
You explained today to [unclear] today

18:28.956 --> 18:31.226
that we start from the roof and then we go down,

18:31.260 --> 18:34.940
not from the firmament we go up, it’s just the same.

18:34.984 --> 18:40.612
It’s India style. It’s a very clever.

19:04.486 --> 19:10.686
Yes, Mother, but she would just like
to ask some questions about Masonry,

19:10.680 --> 19:13.180
but you were talking about Ajanta, and perhaps
it’s better You finish…

19:13.196 --> 19:14.636
That I've finished off

19:14.641 --> 19:17.476
You finish Your talk.

19:17.500 --> 19:25.710
No, I am just saying that the Indians, you see,
have got something about them,

19:25.703 --> 19:28.203
that they are very forgiving.

19:28.203 --> 19:31.913
There is no embitterness in them, they’re very forgiving.

19:31.913 --> 19:35.393
They don’t carry any embitterness in their mind.

19:35.403 --> 19:40.012
And secondly, they are very anonymous.

19:40.012 --> 19:43.483
You will never find name written in any painting.( unclear)

19:43.502 --> 19:46.792
You will never find an Indian
