41:41.906 --> 41:43.556
But she is coming out with another man.

41:43.556 --> 41:46.056
“That’s her brother.” "Oh brother!"

41:46.056 --> 41:47.477
"But doesn’t look like her.”

41:47.501 --> 41:50.001
He said, “That’s her brother, she
has accepted him as a brother.”

41:50.001 --> 41:54.934
But brother cannot travel in
the same coupé, under law.

41:54.934 --> 42:01.944
If there’s a brother and a sister, they
can’t live in one room, under law.

42:01.974 --> 42:05.944
What a filth it is!

42:05.994 --> 42:10.414
Can you imagine? There is no purity
between real brothers and sisters.

42:10.456 --> 42:15.428
Here is just a brother, which..sort of a Rakhi brother.

42:15.448 --> 42:18.158
Imagine, and never goes into our heads.

42:18.158 --> 42:22.537
Nothing, not even my husband’s head,
or his wife’s head or anything.

42:30.352 --> 42:32.677
So, this is something surprising

42:32.677 --> 42:34.162
that people don’t understand

42:34.162 --> 42:38.842
that, as you have to have rules and
regulations for a good civic life,

42:38.865 --> 42:46.459
for good married life also there has to be certain
rules and regulations which are to be respected.

42:46.499 --> 42:51.159
For your good married life, there
has to be some rules and regulations.

43:00.518 --> 43:04.705
Otherwise, how can you have a good married life?

43:04.694 --> 43:07.655
That is not, that is not curbing yourself.

43:07.686 --> 43:14.176
Every freedom has to have certain rules and
regulations so that the freedom is preserved.

43:14.176 --> 43:18.316
For the preservation of the freedom only.

43:19.873 --> 43:22.148
This is abandonment. Licence...

43:22.988 --> 43:24.483
Maryada Purushottama.

43:24.483 --> 43:25.743
Yes.

43:25.743 --> 43:28.243
Maryada Purushottam

43:29.173 --> 43:33.943
This is licence. This is not... this
is in no way freedom. It is licence.

43:35.403 --> 43:37.903
It is abandonment.

43:39.421 --> 43:40.991
Do you see my point?

43:40.991 --> 43:45.301
This is in no way this is freedom.

43:45.331 --> 43:46.331
What is freedom?

43:46.309 --> 43:47.591
The husband is worried about the wife.

43:47.574 --> 43:48.811
Wife is worried about the husband.

43:48.797 --> 43:50.339
Actually, we are free people.

43:50.336 --> 43:52.096
Like my husband goes all over the world

43:52.096 --> 43:53.469
and I know for definite

43:53.443 --> 43:55.413
he is not going to look at any woman.

43:55.434 --> 43:57.223
And he knows for me also,

43:57.229 --> 44:00.743
so we are free people moving everywhere, happily.

44:01.962 --> 44:03.733
This is the true freedom, Mother

44:03.763 --> 44:06.362
It’s the true freedom.

44:06.384 --> 44:09.222
Yes, we are the free people

44:09.249 --> 44:10.329
Supposing now,

44:10.306 --> 44:11.939
he is there, in the house he comes,

44:11.950 --> 44:13.740
if he sleeps in the same bed

44:13.740 --> 44:16.070
my husband won’t doubt it, won't doubt it.

44:16.070 --> 44:17.080
He is like my son.

44:17.080 --> 44:17.990
Of course!

44:17.976 --> 44:20.476
My sons-in-law will come and sleep with me.

44:20.496 --> 44:21.845
You won't believe.

44:22.831 --> 44:24.315
They sleep on the same bed.

44:24.299 --> 44:26.665
“Just hug me, Mummy, Mummy.”

44:26.665 --> 44:27.975
Nobody says anything.

44:27.975 --> 44:29.505
Nobody can even think,

44:29.505 --> 44:32.485
you know, it doesn’t go into our heads.

44:35.335 --> 44:36.375
I can’t understand.

44:36.360 --> 44:38.520
With all this thinking

44:38.520 --> 44:40.420
if people have become mad, like this,

44:40.428 --> 44:41.640
just sex points.

44:41.640 --> 44:43.240
I mean you have reduced yourself to nothing

44:43.240 --> 44:45.740
but sex points.

44:45.740 --> 44:48.240
Think about it? What a degradation!

44:48.240 --> 44:50.740
We were like that before the Realisation.

44:52.120 --> 44:55.650
But now you have become Shri Ganeshas.

44:55.660 --> 44:57.390
You all have become Shri Ganeshas.

44:57.375 --> 44:59.490
You have become such great people now.

44:59.505 --> 45:02.200
But I think, still, I can’t forgive the English

45:02.200 --> 45:04.700
for what they did to You.

45:15.380 --> 45:19.820
English people now has, in South America,

45:19.806 --> 45:23.260
people are [unclear] against English people,

45:23.260 --> 45:25.760
just because of Malvinas. (the Falkland Islands.)

45:25.760 --> 45:26.680
The what?

45:26.697 --> 45:29.940
The war, that they did unto Argentina.

45:29.940 --> 45:31.857
I didn't understand?

45:31.842 --> 45:32.303
Argentina?

45:32.291 --> 45:33.943
Yes, Argentina war with England

45:33.956 --> 45:37.143
The Malvina Islands

45:37.163 --> 45:38.993
That war was... people don't like it

45:38.972 --> 45:43.249
I have seen in all South America,
I usually go by, my job.

45:43.249 --> 45:49.789
Unclear

45:49.839 --> 45:51.338
That was very stupid.

45:51.357 --> 45:54.326
(Tape cuts out and resumes)

45:55.517 --> 45:58.678
Germans were teaching them and
they had those goose steps.

45:58.678 --> 46:01.777
Do you know what is a goose step
is? Left right, left right,

46:01.798 --> 46:04.857
and I asked, "How is it that you know all this?"

46:04.868 --> 46:06.678
They kept quiet.

46:06.678 --> 46:07.848
I said, "This is German."

46:07.848 --> 46:13.738
And there are lots of Germans who have built
up their bases there, horrible Germans.

46:13.768 --> 46:17.043
So in a way, it is I agree
that they should not have,

46:17.043 --> 46:18.793
but Argentina is saved,

46:18.761 --> 46:23.191
because these Germans would
have really finished them off.

46:25.678 --> 46:28.009
On Friday, I have been in Buenos Aires

46:28.017 --> 46:30.189
I came to the Puja.

46:30.187 --> 46:35.807
And I feel now, there is a group waiting for You

46:35.817 --> 46:38.857
or maybe waiting for me to make the decision.

46:38.866 --> 46:41.706
I spoke about You and they are really waiting.

46:41.695 --> 46:45.926
They’ll get it. They’ll get it, because,
you see, their prestige has gone.

46:45.926 --> 46:48.176
Argentina is in the UN, and all that.

46:48.177 --> 46:51.711
They have not lost much prestige.
English has lost prestige more.

46:51.711 --> 46:55.093
But the Germans are finished.

46:55.083 --> 46:57.363
They were horrible people there, Germans.

46:57.339 --> 47:01.373
And Germans were training all their
military, all their navy, everything.

47:01.373 --> 47:03.873
They have built a huge, big barricade,

47:03.873 --> 47:06.983
which I have seen Myself

47:07.013 --> 47:08.653
and I was quite frightened.

47:08.652 --> 47:10.713
So, in a way it's good.

47:10.713 --> 47:16.447
In a way it’s good, in a way also
Argentina has not lost prestige.

47:16.457 --> 47:18.277
So it's alright. Doesn’t matter.

47:18.311 --> 47:23.377
In the war, though, English has won the
war, Argentina has not lost its face, no doubt.

47:23.397 --> 47:25.897
People feel that Argentina was not wrong,

47:25.897 --> 47:28.397
in keeping Falklands.

47:28.397 --> 47:32.317
And still, there is a lot of
reaction against Mrs Thatcher.

47:32.317 --> 47:37.427
The other day they were asking her,
“How did you bombard that ship?"

47:37.427 --> 47:39.927
People detest Mrs Thatcher.

47:41.897 --> 47:46.345
The truth of the real aggressiveness
is coming out now in the war files.

47:46.357 --> 47:52.035
It is all being exposed, as to how they
overdid the boundaries of normal defense.

47:52.018 --> 47:53.645
Changing the course of the ship also,

47:53.645 --> 47:57.625
the ship went and bombarded
and two hundred sixty-five (unclear)

47:57.625 --> 48:00.125
So all this, prestige wise they have not lost.

48:00.125 --> 48:02.625
But these Germans are reduced
I am very happy about them,

48:02.625 --> 48:05.125
because these Germans, if you
allow them to grow like that.

48:05.125 --> 48:07.625
They are still in Chile, Mother, now.

48:07.605 --> 48:10.626
They are still in Chile now.

48:10.657 --> 48:11.146
Chile

48:11.146 --> 48:13.646
They have moved in Chile?

48:13.666 --> 48:18.917
They are now there, with Pinochet
and all these people, doing the same.

48:18.927 --> 48:26.067
But Chile people are also…Chile
government is very, very tough government.

48:26.077 --> 48:28.337
Shri Mataji, they’d like to give you dinner now.

48:28.337 --> 48:29.939
All right?

48:29.939 --> 48:33.749
Thank You very much for talking to us.

48:47.559 --> 48:51.587
I’m going to eat what you have brought for me.
